These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
There 4 different types of food: orange, lime, grapefruit, cucumber
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, french, german, colombian
House: modern, palace, craftsman, wooden
1. the modern house is the person eating cucumber##1
2. the craftsman house is on the left of the french##1
3. the person eating cucumber is in an odd position##4
4. the palace house is on the left or right of the wooden house##3
5. the german is on the left or right of the person eating orange##3
6. the wooden house is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
7. the palace house is on the far left or far right##3
8. the wooden house is between the colombian and the person eating orange##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Food         | cucumber      | orange | lime | grapefruit |
| Nationality   | german | spanish  | french   | colombian    |
| House     | modern     | craftsman    | wooden    | palace      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, juice, milk
4 different games are played: chess, whist, mah-jongg, scrabble
4 different pets are kept: turtle, cat, goat, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
2. the person drinking milk is the person playing mah-jongg##1
3. the person drinking juice is in an even position##4
4. the owner of the turtle is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left##1
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person playing whist##1
7. the person playing chess is between the person drinking milk and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
8. the person playing scrabble is between the person playing whist and the person drinking juice##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Beverage         | milk | juice   | hot-chocolate | cola  |
| Game   | mah-jongg     | chess | scrabble  | whist |
| Pet     | guinea-pig        | goat  | cat    | turtle |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, april, june, february
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, iris, daffodil, dahlia
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, documentary, adventure, action
1. the person who growsdahlia is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who's birthday is in february##2
2. the person who growsiris is the person watching action movies##1
3. the person watching horror movies is the person who's birthday is in june##1
4. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
5. the person who's birthday is in february is in an odd position##4
6. the person who growsdaffodil is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who growsorchid##2
7. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Birthday          | december | april   | february     | june     |
| Flower   | iris  | dahlia | daffodil   | orchid  |
| Movie-Genre     | action      | documentary | adventure | horror |

