.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, spanish, pakistani, indonesian
House: cape-cod, townhouse, tower, futuristic
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, rock-climbing, hiking, singing
1. the futuristic house is in an even position##4
2. the spanish is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
4. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the pakistani##3
5. the futuristic house is the person who's hobby is camping##1
6. the pakistani is the cape-cod house##1
7. the tower house is the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Nationality   | nigerian  | indonesian   | pakistani     | spanish |
| House   | tower  | futuristic      | cape-cod        | townhouse     |
| Hobby         | hiking | camping | singing | rock-climbing   |

