.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, old-henry, montecristo, bluemaster
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, trance, classical, dubstep
There 4 different types of food: peach, lettuce, grapefruit, pineapple
1. the bluemaster-smoker is the fan of dubstep##1
2. the montecristo-smoker is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating peach is the fan of dubstep##1
4. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
5. the person eating peach is in an even position##4
6. the fan of trance is on the far left##1
7. the old-henry-smoker is on the far right##1
8. the montecristo-smoker is on the left or right of the person eating grapefruit##3
9. the fan of r&b is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Cigar   | swisher   | bluemaster   | montecristo | old-henry |
| Music-Genre         | trance      | dubstep | r&b      | classical |
| Food     | lettuce | peach        | pineapple       | grapefruit  |

