.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, orchid, lily, rose
City: new-york, san-francisco, rome, marseilles
4 different games are played: poker, monopoly, backgammon, bridge
1. the person who growsorchid is in an odd position##4
2. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
3. the person playing poker is the person who growsorchid##1
4. the person who growslily is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
5. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far right##1
6. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
7. the person who growsrose is in an even position##4
8. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Flower    | lily   | rose      | orchid       | balloon-flower |
| City   | new-york | marseilles | rome     | san-francisco |
| Game     | bridge     | monopoly  | poker | backgammon |

