.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, vegafina, bolivar, alhambra
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, daisy, dahlia, poppy
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, lime, cherry, potato
1. the person eating cherry is the person who growsdaffodil##1
2. the person eating lime is between the person who growspoppy and the person eating nectarine##2
3. the person who growspoppy is the vegafina-smoker##1
4. the person who growsdaisy is on the left or right of the vegafina-smoker##3
5. the davidoff-smoker is in an even position##4
6. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
7. the person who growsdaffodil is the davidoff-smoker##1
8. the person eating cherry is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Cigar      | bolivar   | alhambra          | vegafina | davidoff        |
| Flower   | dahlia     | daisy | poppy   | daffodil     |
| Food           | nectarine | lime         | potato         | cherry |

