.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
4 different pets are kept: horse, frog, guinea-pig, mouse
House: cape-cod, futuristic, art-deco, cottage
4 different games are played: domino, canasta, scrabble, snooker
1. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3
2. the art-deco house is the owner of the horse##1
3. the cottage house is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
5. the person playing canasta is between the cape-cod house and the owner of the horse##2
6. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
7. the owner of the horse is in an even position##4
8. the owner of the horse is between the owner of the frog and the owner of the guinea-pig##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Pet         | frog | horse      | guinea-pig       | mouse    |
| House           | futuristic  | art-deco  | cottage | cape-cod |
| Game   | snooker      | scrabble | canasta         | domino    |

