City: nizza, new-york, paris, prague
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, ritmeester, pall-mall, montecristo
1. the person traveling to nizza is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the person traveling to nizza##3
3. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the person traveling to nizza##3
4. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
5. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the pall-mall-smoker##3
6. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
7. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
8. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
9. the person traveling to prague is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Pet   | snake         | rabbit  | turtle     | frog         |
| City        | prague | new-york | nizza | paris         |
| Cigar      | ritmeester         | pall-mall  | game   | montecristo |

