.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, mechanic, writer, bartender
4 different games are played: billiard, poker, go, mah-jongg
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, mirinda, coffee, tea
 1. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the writer##3
 2. the person playing billiard is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the mechanic##1
 4. the person playing go is between the mechanic and the dancer##2
 5. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the mechanic##3
 6. the person drinking tea is the writer##1
 7. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far right##1
 8. the dancer is in an odd position##4
 9. the person playing poker is between the bartender and the writer##2
10. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Job   | dancer  | writer    | mechanic | bartender    |
| Game   | billiard | go | poker  | mah-jongg |
| Beverage           | coffee   | tea    | milk        | mirinda   |

