.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
4 different games are played: canasta, mah-jongg, bridge, billiard
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, november, december, march
House: wooden, townhouse, futuristic, ranch-style
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
2. the person playing bridge is on the far left##1
3. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the ranch-style house##3
4. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
5. the wooden house is between the person who's birthday is in march and the ranch-style house##2
6. the person who's birthday is in december is in an even position##4
7. the person playing canasta is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Game          | bridge    | mah-jongg  | billiard  | canasta |
| Birthday   | march | november | july | december |
| House   | futuristic    | wooden     | ranch-style    | townhouse |

