.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, time-travel, musical, fantasy
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, snowmobile, roller, tram
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, volleyball, skiing, golf
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person watching musical movies and the person driving the airplane##2
2. the person watching crime movies is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
4. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is in an odd position##4
6. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
7. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3
8. the person driving the roller is the person watching crime movies##1
9. the person driving the tram is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who's sport is parkour##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre      | crime | musical      | time-travel  | fantasy    |
| Transport   | roller   | snowmobile | tram | airplane |
| Sport           | golf      | skiing       | volleyball   | parkour      |

