3. the person watching musical movies is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person driving the subway is in an even position##4
5. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
6. the owner of the horse is between the person watching epic movies and the owner of the rat##2
7. the person watching musical movies is on the far right##1
8. the owner of the chinchilla is in an even position##4
9. the person watching epic movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
