.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-16::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, time-travel, superhero, spy
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, blood-red, emerald, azure
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, nigerian, mexican, malaysian
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3
2. the person who likes aquamarine is in an even position##4
3. the malaysian is on the far left##1
4. the person who likes blood-red is on the left or right of the person watching spy movies##3
5. the person watching time-travel movies is between the nigerian and the person who likes emerald##2
6. the chinese is the person who likes azure##1
7. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
8. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre    | superhero    | time-travel     | martial-arts    | spy        |
| Color       | emerald   | aquamarine | blood-red | azure |
| Nationality   | malaysian | mexican      | nigerian    | chinese   |

