4. the person drinking cola is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
6. the person drinking cola is in an odd position##4
7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person drinking sprite is the person who growsmarigold##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |    4     |
