.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, train, roller, skateboard
City: marseilles, nizza, liverpool, venice
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, lemonade, soy-milk, hot-chocolate
1. the person driving the airplane is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to venice is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person traveling to marseilles##3
4. the person driving the roller is on the far left##1
5. the person driving the train is between the person traveling to venice and the person traveling to marseilles##2
6. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
8. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Transport    | roller    | train    | airplane  | skateboard |
| City   | venice | nizza | marseilles | liverpool      |
| Beverage     | lemonade   | almond-milk        | hot-chocolate   | soy-milk       |

 